s. Has a fair record when second up, including three top-three finishes. This looks a sterner test than last time but with added fitness he is capable of a big performance. 6. HONOUR WHIM resumes from a spell of five-and-a-half months and is having her first outing under new trainer Romy Van Der Meulen. Finished eighth at Ascot over 2011m at the opening run last time in work. Sound top-three prospects. 7. DELIGHTED is back after a break of five months. At the last run before the layoff she finished eighth over 2200m at Krefeld. Solid top-three hope.\",\"runners\":[2,1,6,7],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Wett Star Germany","tipRunnerNumbers":[7,2,3]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,6,3]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,6,1,4]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,5,2]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,4,2,1]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,2,4,6]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,4,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,3,4]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"DDF","raceType":"R"}}]}}}